#. Tag: refpurpose
#: man-xml2pot.1.docbook:19
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creates a PO template file from a DocBook XML file."
msgstr "Opretter en PO-skabelon-fil ud fra en DocBook XML-fil."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: man-xml2pot.1.docbook:23
#, no-c-format
